  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Pattern B — PEF/Carbon footprint DECLARATION (master data).",
    "",
    "The brand has computed the PEFCR Apparel & Footwear single score once for",
    "this SKU and publishes it as part of the product's master data. Every",
    "unit of GTIN 09521234000013 carries the same declaration; the EPCIS event",
    "itself (here a commissioning) only marks the point at which the unit",
    "enters the regulated supply chain. environmentalFootprint therefore lives",
    "INSIDE masterDataAvailableFor on the product entry.",
    "",
    "Use this pattern when: the score is the product's authoritative published",
    "PEF declaration that travels with every unit of the SKU.",
    "Use the observation pattern (observation-carbon-footprint.jsonld) when:",
    "the score may differ across lots / inspections, or the event itself is",
    "what produced the value.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,textile=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/textile/",
    "See: core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
